{"type":null,"faqId":17875,"title":"忘记屏幕解锁密码或图案","answer":"<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">您可以通过升级手机的方法解决。升级后，手机内部存储中的数据将被删除。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">microSD</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卡升级：</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Book Antiqua', serif;\">步骤 1<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">进入华为终端官网\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm;\"><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn\" title=\" \"><span style=\"font-family:'Frutiger Next Com','sans-serif';color:black;layout-grid-mode:both;text-decoration:none;\ntext-underline:none\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Book Antiqua', serif;\">步骤 2<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">将升级包放入\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">dload</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">文件夹下，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">dload</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">文件夹需要在 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">microSD</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卡的根目录下手动创建。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Book Antiqua', serif;\">步骤 3<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">手机在关机状态下，插入\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">microS</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">D</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -3cm; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卡，同时按住电源键和音量上下键直到出现安卓机器人图标，手机进入升级模式开始升级。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">升级完成后手机将会恢复出厂设置。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; line-height: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">----</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; line-height: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">结束</span>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">若无法升级，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n<p>\n<br>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"655","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420340374000,"seriesProductName":"SC-CL00","visitedTimes":655,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}